column2: The many flaws of the Eldar Avatar in classic 40k
column7:
Today we learn about the Eldar Avatar. Was it a game breaking beast or has it always been a bit of a mess on the tabletop?

This video was filmed before I started experimented with AI enhanced images so its a little rough in places. Also, editing videos has been a bit of a learning experience so it will seem a bit clunky as well,  let me know if you spot anything out of the ordinary.
